{"tid":739490,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[食鬼食評]—danish bar","createTime":"2018-07-12T06:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T16:03:54.000Z","uid":182683,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"278dafa906fc2ce63cbf0952ab385c366fb179e5","tid":739490,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:54:13.000Z","msg":"地點：觀塘apm danish bar<br />\n<br />\n第一次聽danish bar，試試佢先。甜品黎講唔好同我攪咁多花臣又拉絲又紫薯咩咩係到搞哩搞路，見到就火！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/145138_fa6dad5f3989bcd98a2404b998603920.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F145138_fa6dad5f3989bcd98a2404b998603920.png&h=efd15154&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/145144_f25771beac67db07dc271898f8e2514e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F145144_f25771beac67db07dc271898f8e2514e.png&h=43194db7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n買左條crunch sugar danish bar $17蚊，個樣成轆野咁，面有d令令地應該係crunch sugar glaze。<br />\n第一次食啲咁既野。。。完美融合左p&acirc;t&eacute; de choux同danish兩種pastry，外面極脆，入面係danish先有既honey comb structure，好light，食落有啲麵粉既麥香味同好重牛油味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢仲有超多唔同味，下次一定要試曬佢！<br />\n法國依間野比人低估得好緊要！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n評分：7/10<br />\n評語：懷疑係麵包之神東和馬既出品！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIg:hkfoodghost<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e38e1186c590df9e861d268019ac48908b1a37","tid":739490,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T07:46:16.000Z","msg":"Ig可唔